With some projects I have problem with symfony-demo/config/routes/dev/twig.yaml.
I believe it's because error move from '@TwigBundle/Resources/config/routing/errors.xml' to 'framework-bundle/Resources/config/routing/errors.xml' (and replace twig.yaml by framework.yaml).

